__SqlaTable__.sql:
SELECT DISTINCT observationdatetime, license_plate
FROM default.surat_itms_live live inner join default.network_issue_regions network on live.route_id=network.route_id 
-- where observationdatetime >=  ((date_add('minute', 330, localtimestamp)) - interval '1' hour)
